lobal_Objects/Object/__lookupGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupGetter__()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupSetter__()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/hasOwnProperty\"><code>Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/isPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.prototype.isPrototypeOf()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/propertyIsEnumerable\"><code>Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/setPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.setPrototypeOf()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toLocaleString\"><code>Object.prototype.toLocaleString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/valueOf\"><code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><strong><code>RegExp[@@species]</code></strong> アクセサープロパティは <code>RegExp</code> コンストラクターを返します。</p>\n\n<div id=\"sect2\"><iframe class=\"interactive\" height=\"490\" src=\"https://interactive-examples.mdn.mozilla.net/pages/js/regexp-getregexp-@@species.html\" title=\"MDN Web Docs Interactive Example\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"description","title":"解説","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>species</code> アクセサープロパティは、 <code>RegExp</code> の既定のコンストラクターを返します。サブクラスのコンストラクターは、コンストラクターの割り当てをオーバーライドするためにこれを使用することができます。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"species_in_ordinary_objects","title":"通常オブジェクトの species","isH3":true,"content":"<p><code>species</code> プロパティは、既定のコンストラクターを返します。 <code>RegExp</code> オブジェクトであれば、 <code>RegExp</code> コンストラクターを返します。</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>RegExp<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>Symbol<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>species<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// function RegExp()</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"species_in_derived_objects","title":"派生オブジェクトの species","isH3":true,"content":"<p>派生クラスのコレクションオブジェクト (たとえば、独自の正規表現を表す <code>MyRegExp</code>) では、 <code>MyRegExp</code> の species は <code>MyRegExp</code> コンストラクターです。しかし、派生クラスのメソッドで親である <code>RegExp</code> オブジェクトを返すようにこれをオーバーライドしたくなるかもしれません。</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">MyRegExp</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">RegExp</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// MyRegExp の species を親である RegExp コンストラクタにオーバーライドします。</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">get</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>Symbol<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>species<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> RegExp<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"仕様書","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様書</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://tc39.es/ecma262/#sec-get-regexp-@@species\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript (ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"ja\">get RegExp [ @@species ] の定義</small></a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"javascript.builtins.RegExp.@@species","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/RegExp/@@species/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect4\">\n<p></p><p></p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/RegExp\"><code>RegExp</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Symbol/species\"><code>Symbol.species</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"解説","id":"description"},{"text":"例","id":"examples"},{"text":"仕様書","id":"specifications"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"RegExp[@@species] アクセサープロパティは RegExp コンストラクターを返します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"get RegExp[@@species]","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"get RegExp[@@species]","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"get RegExp[@@species]","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/regexp/@@species","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/regexp/@@species/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"paren